# Guidelines

- Follow [docs/03-architecture/design-spec.md](../../docs/03-architecture/design-spec.md) for Human + Agent framework.
- API work → read `pcampus-rest-api` skill; update `docs/03-architecture/api/`.
- Tests → `pcampus-testing` skill + goal test plan.
- Before closing a goal → `pcampus-code-review` checklist.
- Deploy / staging goals → `pcampus-deploy-staging` skill.
- Schema changes → `pcampus-db-migration` skill + `docs/03-architecture/data/`.
- Incidents → `pcampus-incident-response` skill; human owns comms and production actions.
- Stack-specific rules: copy `.cursor/rules/stack-*.example.mdc` → `{stack}.mdc` at bootstrap.
- Governance: [governance.mdc](governance.mdc) · Security: [security.mdc](security.mdc)

Full skill catalog: [docs/04-agents/skills-library.md](../../docs/04-agents/skills-library.md).
